(23, 68, 1141588948, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 3, 0, 6, 1141584866, 5, 3, 2006, 1141591603, 5, 3, 2006, 'published', 0, 'Bill''s wonderful wife, Arynne Simon,', '&nbsp; <p style="text-align: justify"><span style="font-size: 8pt; font-family: Arial">Bill&#39;s wonderful wife, Arynne Simon, also has a warm place I appreciate her love, kindness, and generosity that she has shown last three years. My only disappointing experience is not enjoy her great cooking. Now that the book is finally finished, can convince her to cook a celebration dinner!</span></p><p style="text-align: justify"><span style="font-size: 8pt; font-family: Arial">Having been so focused on The Art of Intrusion,I haven&#39;t much quality time with family and close friends. I became what of a workaholic, similar to the days where I&#39;d spend countless the keyboard exploring the dark corners of cyberspace. </span></p>'),
(24, 66, 1141600594, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 3, 0, 6, 1141582569, 5, 3, 2006, 1141600772, 5, 3, 2006, 'published', 0, 'Most of stories appear in this book', '<p class="\\"><span>With hackers, checking the bona fides is tricky. Most of stories appear in this book, other than a few who have to prison, would face felony charges if their true identities So, asking for real names, or expecting to be is an iffy proposition.</span></p><p class="\\"><span>These people have only come forward with their stories because me. They know I&rsquo;ve done time myself, and they are willing my not betraying them in a way that could put them in that Yet, despite the risks, many did offer tangible proof of their hacks.</span></p><p class="\\"><span>Even so, it&rsquo;s possible&mdash;in fact, it&rsquo;s likely&mdash;that some people ated their stories with details intended to make them more compelling,</span></p><p class="\\"><span>or spun a story that was a total fabrication, but constructed workable exploits to give them the ring of truth.</span></p><p class="\\"><span>Because of that risk, we have been diligent in holding to a dard of reliability. Through all the interviews, I have challenged detail, asking for in-depth explanations of anything </span></p><p class="\\"><span>sound quite right, and sometimes following up later to see still the same or if he or she told it differently the Or, if this person &ldquo;couldn&rsquo;t remember&rdquo; when asked to-accomplish step omitted from the story. Or, if this seem to know enough to do what he or she claimed how he or she got from point A to point B.</span></p><span>Except where specifically noted, every one of the main stories has passed my <font color="#00f000">&ldquo;</font><font color="#003000"><font color="#00f000"><span>smell test</span></font>.</font>&rdquo; My co-author and I agreed of every person whose story we have included. </span>'),
