(2, 'About the ENBR (El Nuevo Bantay Radyo)', '<p>DYDD EL Nuevo Bantay Radyo is one of the many local AM stations here in Cebu City. The station&#39;s new office in Escario St. has housed at least 37 employees including those field technicians and engineers who were assigned at the transmitter site. </p><p>Founded and operated in 1995 by the Siam Broadcasting which is presently based in Cagayan de Oro City. Today, the station hosts 2 relaying stations namely DYHH in Bogo, Cebu and DYZZ in Guihulngan, Negros Oriental. The relaying stations have program formats the same as the host station - the DYDD. Due to the demands, the station will extend its operation launching another sister station in Davao City next year. </p><p>The station coexists through the management of the Lacto-PAFI Corporation, dealers of health drinks, owned and managed by Engr. Gregorio Sanchez. The Lacto PAFI products had been a constant client of the station but it has also served small to big scale establishments for its advertisement needs. </p><p>Comments? Suggestions? Criticisms? We would love to hear your feedback.&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Address:</strong> <br />Escario St. Cebu City </p><p><strong>Contact No:</strong><br />+63 2 897 5145/46 </p><p><strong>Fax No:</strong><br />(02) 527 9653 up to 54 </p><p><strong>Email:</strong> <br />admin@enbr.com </p><p><strong>Office Hours:</strong><br />9:00 a.m. to 9:00 p.m. GMT+8 (Mondays to Fridays) </p>', 'Published', 1143623518, 0, 1, 0),
